  31 Mar 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> peppercorn-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Add support for the new PyPy slotting.

  05 Sep 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> peppercorn-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Clean up PYTHON_COMPAT from old implementations.

*peppercorn-0.4-r1 (16 Aug 2013)

  16 Aug 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +peppercorn-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Migrate to distutils-r1.

*peppercorn-0.4 (22 Feb 2012)

  22 Feb 2012; Marien Zwart <marienz@gentoo.org> +peppercorn-0.4.ebuild:
  Version bump, adding Python 3 support.

*peppercorn-0.3 (30 Jul 2011)

  30 Jul 2011; Rafael G. Martins <rafaelmartins@gentoo.org>
  +peppercorn-0.3.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  Initial version. Based on ebuild by Jan Matějka (bug #368013).
